data.description: Limestone Schools! Not your typical tri-level home; this one has so much space! Peaceful setting and large backyard. The deck is off the dining area/kitchen overlooking the beautiful pool and entertaining space. This is the perfect spot for that morning coffee and also to entertain friends and family this summer! Bedrooms are all oversized and offer great closet space. One bedroom is set up as a walk-in closet or "getting ready" room with built-ins. Its a definite must see! Lower level offers a family room with fireplace. Garage has extra attic storage. Fantastic neighborhood and location. AC/Furnace are new, Water Heater is also new! Electrical has been upgraded to 200AMP service. This home is truly a must see!
